&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About WPP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WPP is the trusted growth partner for the world’s leading brands. We unite&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge media intelligence and data solutions, world-class creativity, next-generation production, transformative enterprise solutions and expert strategic counsel&amp;nbsp;in a single company –&amp;nbsp;powered by exceptional talent and our agentic marketing platform, WPP Open,&amp;nbsp;to help our clients navigate change, capture opportunity and deliver transformational growth. For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wpp.com/&quot; data-outlook-id=&quot;7b8142a7-a6db-4263-9929-267c84e3fdd8&quot;&gt;WPP.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The opportunity:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;A commercially astute and consultatively minded &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Client Success Partner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; to join our client leadership team. This is a senior advisory role at the heart of how we create value for our clients — translating complex analytical work into strategic guidance that directly shapes our clients&#39; investment decisions and growth trajectories.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You are a trusted advisor&amp;nbsp;first and foremost&amp;nbsp;— someone who builds genuine partnerships with senior client stakeholders, earns a seat at the table through deep&amp;nbsp;expertise, and brings the intellectual curiosity and commercial instinct to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;where Gain Theory can make a meaningful difference.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You will bring &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;12+ years of experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; in marketing effectiveness, analytics, or a related consulting discipline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;14&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Acting as a Strategic Advisor to Senior Clients:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; You&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;be the primary consultative voice for your clients — proactively shaping how they think about marketing investment, effectiveness measurement, and growth. You&amp;nbsp;won&#39;t&amp;nbsp;wait

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About WPP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WPP is the trusted growth partner for the world’s leading brands. We unite&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge media intelligence and data solutions, world-class creativity, next-generation production, transformative enterprise solutions and expert strategic counsel&amp;nbsp;in a single company –&amp;nbsp;powered by exceptional talent and our agentic marketing platform, WPP Open,&amp;nbsp;to help our clients navigate change, capture opportunity and deliver transformational growth. For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wpp.com/&quot; data-outlook-id=&quot;7b8142a7-a6db-4263-9929-267c84e3fdd8&quot;&gt;WPP.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The opportunity:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support senior colleagues in achieving the efficient delivery of client projects. Typical responsibilities and duties are the collection and preparation of data, contributing to the finalisation of models, writing results and implications and SFX creation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your role as Principal Analyst is to take responsibility for and oversee other analysts. You will also be expected support the development of analysts through the Training Academy, Knowledge Shares and feedback. Principal Analysts should develop relationships with their counterparts client side and be able to communicate Gain Theory approaches and brand beliefs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Working with data:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Data extraction and manipulation, data analysis and validation, batch files, programming&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Undertake data extraction, manipulation, and data analysis to understand the marketplace and client context relevant to each project.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Analyse all datasets to ensure that each KPI is understood and can be explained back to the team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ensure that all tables, charts and other information produced by you, or others has been checked for accuracy and formatted to GT standards before passing on to senior project team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Be responsible for data collection including preparation and sending of data requests, chasing outstanding data and querying data with clients and agencies.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ensure that ROVA input files are structured to meet requirements of project (e.g. order and number of variables, exclusion of unnecessary variables)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ensure that all outputs are checked for accuracy by analysts; record any checks made.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Proficiency in using data extraction tools (i.e. Advantage, AdDynamix, Sysomos, Google Trends, Google Analytics, Double Click) and able to teach others in their use. Be aware of alternatives and the PROs / CONs of the tool.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Proficiency in using Excel/SQL/Python/Pandas/Analytics Workbench to process, transform, create variables and build models. Be or be working towards expert knowledge in a selection of these tools / approaches.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Building Models:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Model building and validation, sales effects calculations, ROIs, media optimisation&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Oversee the building of comprehensive base models according to the project specification, incorporating all drivers of KPIs, providing rationale for variables entered, understanding coefficients and SFX.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Taking base models, oversee or build in additional improvements and progress the model towards finalization.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About WPP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WPP is the trusted growth partner for the world’s leading brands. We unite&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge media intelligence and data solutions, world-class creativity, next-generation production, transformative enterprise solutions and expert strategic counsel&amp;nbsp;in a single company –&amp;nbsp;powered by exceptional talent and our agentic marketing platform, WPP Open,&amp;nbsp;to help our clients navigate change, capture opportunity and deliver transformational growth. For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wpp.com/&quot; data-outlook-id=&quot;7b8142a7-a6db-4263-9929-267c84e3fdd8&quot;&gt;WPP.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The opportunity:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Senior Client Success Director with deep expertise in Marketing effectiveness and econometrics to lead our most strategic client relationships and shape the future of our client success function. In this senior leadership role, you will serve as a trusted advisor to C-suite executives, ensuring our advanced analytics solutions deliver measurable business outcomes while driving account growth and retention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Client Success Senior Director will be responsible for client leadership across a selection of Gain Theory’s portfolio. The ideal candidate should have a minimum of 8 years of experience in client relationship management and data analytics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We expect this person to be the primary point of contact for senior client stakeholders and to act as a trusted advisor, deeply understanding client business objectives and leveraging Gain Theory’s expertise to deliver exceptional value and drive measurable results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require someone who has a deep understanding of data and analytics, is able to interpret complex datasets and extract actionable insights that drive client success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This person should serve as an inspirational leader within the Client Success team, fostering a collaborative and results-oriented environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Project Delivery:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures projects within remit are managed to time and scope. Highlights any risks to client lead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Puts in place robust quality assurance techniques and follows them to ensure work going to clients is right first time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uses data and analytics interpretation skills to bring insights to life for a mid-senior audience (i.e. most senior day-to-day client stakeholder)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is a strong data storyteller who can explain complex insights at a simple, impactful level to a variety of audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures clients have full knowledge and training of Gain Theory Interactive, highlighting any bugs or enhancements to the GTI team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures projects are following Operational Excellence process and that there is full adherence from Client Success team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Financial:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;​Looks for opportunities to drive profitable growth for clients and take on incremental (e.g. 1-30% growth) opportunities. Bring in client lead and senior team for larger opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies values driven for clients and looks to assist clients in recognising that value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands how decisions made on projects will impact profitability and looks to run more efficient processes or tighter management of scope, designed in consultancy with client lead.&lt;/li&gt;
